mixin card-sing-in()
  .card-sing-in
    .card-sing-in__content
      h1.card-sing-in__title
        | Войти
      form.card-sing-in__form
        .card-sing-in__item.card-sing-in__item_margin-b-10
          +textField(
            {
              title: '', 
              placeholder: 'Email', 
              type: 'email', 
              required: true

            }
          )
        .card-sing-in__item.card-sing-in__item_margin-b-30
          +textField(
            {
              title: '', 
              placeholder: 'Пароль', 
              type: 'text', 
              required: true,
              pat: '(?=^.{8,}$)((?=.*\d)|(?=.*\W+))(?![.\n])(?=.*[A-Z])(?=.*[a-z]).*$'
            }
          )
        button.button.button_big.card-sing-in__button-in Войти
        .card-sing-in__check-in 
          span.card-sing-in__check-in-text
            | Нет аккаунта на Toxin?
          a(href="registration-page.html").button.button_white Создать